### Departments List
GET http://localhost:5000/api/departments?page=1&limit=10

### Department Details
GET http://localhost:5000/api/departments/{{departmentId}}

### Create Department
POST http://localhost:5000/api/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Operations",
  "code": "OPS",
  "description": "Operations department"
}

### Users List
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users?page=1&limit=10&search=Rahul

### Create User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": "EMP100",
  "fullName": "Test Employee",
  "email": "test.employee@assetflow.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "EMPLOYEE",
  "departmentId": "{{departmentId}}"
}

### Assets List
GET http://localhost:5000/api/assets?page=1&limit=10&search=LAP

### Create Asset
POST http://localhost:5000/api/assets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetTag": "LAP-999",
  "name": "Demo Laptop",
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "ownerDepartmentId": "{{departmentId}}",
  "locationCode": "IT-01",
  "status": "AVAILABLE",
  "condition": "NEW",
  "isBookable": false
}
